collections.name: Chinese Zodiac Maidens
collections.description:
This series of works takes the Chinese traditional zodiac as the theme and skillfully integrates zodiac elements with the images of girls.
In terms of styling design, each girl wears a magnificent headdress corresponding to her zodiac - animal. The majesty of the tiger, the agility of the rabbit, the dominance of the dragon, and other characteristics are exquisitely presented through the headdresses. The costumes adopt a traditional Chinese style, with exquisite patterns and vivid colors. The main colors of orange and blue create a strong visual impact, combining traditional charm with modern aesthetics.
In terms of cultural connotations, while showcasing the unique charm of the twelve zodiac animals, the works inherit and promote traditional Chinese culture, presenting the ancient zodiac culture in a novel and fascinating way and achieving a perfect unity of traditional culture and fashionable art.
